        public MapGraph​(String osmPath,
                String placesPath,
                org.locationtech.spatial4j.context.SpatialContext context)
         throws ParserConfigurationException,
                SAXException,
                IOException
        Constructs a new map graph from the path to an OSM GZ file and a places TSV.
        Parameters:
        osmPath - The path to a gzipped OSM (XML) file.
        placesPath - The path to a TSV file representing places and importance.
        Throws:
        ParserConfigurationException - if a parser cannot be created.
        SAXException - for SAX errors.
        IOException - if a file is not found or if the file is not gzipped.
